text: My Ex and Whys is a 2017 Filipino South Korean romantic comedy movie directed by Cathy Garcia-Molina and starring Enrique Gil, Liza Soberano, Joey Marquez, Cai Cortez, Ara Mina, Ryan Bang, Dominic Roque. It was distributed by Star Cinema. ==Other websites== * Category:2017 romantic comedy movies Category:Filipino movies Category:South Korean movies Category:Movies directed by Cathy Garcia-Molina
